title.rendered: Casa Munras Garden Hotel & Spa Announces Custom Meeting Package

content.rendered:
— Meetings Made to Order–

MONTEREY, Calif., Jan. 8, 2024 /PRNewswire/ — At Casa Munras Garden Hotel & Spa, we bring spirit to your event, whether you’re hosting a business retreat, corporate meeting, or association presentation.  Our Custom Meeting Package makes planning a breeze and provides optional concessions for your specific needs. Located in the heart of historic downtown Monterey Casa Munras features 5,500 square feet of flexible meeting space, award-winning food & beverage, stylish guestrooms, onsite full day spa and a convenient downtown location.  The on-site sales team helps ensure meeting objectives are met and attendees are inspired.

Originally published at https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/casa-munras-garden-hotel–spa-announces-custom-meeting-package-302028992.html
Images courtesy of https://pixabay.com
